protected_spaces_details.description: Provision for children and young people

description: Demolition of Dudley House and Nos. 139-147 Harrow Road; erection of five storey building fronting Harrow Road, a 14 storey tower and six storey building fronting North Wharf Road, comprising a total of 88 residential units (38 affordable and 50 private residential units); ground floor (Class D1) social and community use; flexible ground floor active frontage (Class A1-A3 and  A4); basement car parking,provision of shared amenity space, play area and landscaping. (Council's Own  Development)
